    public static final String CAMEL_SOURCE_FILE_ENDPOINT_READ_LOCK_DELETE_ORPHAN_LOCK_FILES_DOC = "Whether or not read lock with marker files should upon startup delete any orphan read lock files, which may have been left on the file system, if Camel was not properly shutdown (such as a JVM crash). If turning this option to false then any orphaned lock file will cause Camel to not attempt to pickup that file, this could also be due another node is concurrently reading files from the same shared directory.";
